                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Et si nos coupables ancêtres",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Ont eu de coupables enfants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "O triste muse de l'histoire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Ne grave plus à la mémoire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Ce qui doit périr à jamais !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Tu n'as vu qu'horreur et délire.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Les annales de chaque empire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Sont les archives des forfaits.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si la main des rois et des prêtres\nÉbranla le monde en tout temps,\nEt si nos coupables ancêtres\nOnt eu de coupables enfants,\nO triste muse de l'histoire,\nNe grave plus à la mémoire\nCe qui doit périr à jamais !\nTu n'as vu qu'horreur et délire.\nLes annales de chaque empire\nSont les archives des forfaits."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
