                    "line_text": "N'épouvantez plus les mortels.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Que je hais le divin Achille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Sa colère en malheurs fertile,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Et tous ces ridicules dieux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Que vers le ruisseau du Scamandre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Du haut du ciel on fait descendre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Pour inspirer un furieux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La Fable est encor plus funeste ;\nSes mensonges sont plus cruels.\nTantale, Atrée, Égisthe, Oreste,\nN'épouvantez plus les mortels.\nQue je hais le divin Achille,\nSa colère en malheurs fertile,\nEt tous ces ridicules dieux\nQue vers le ruisseau du Scamandre\nDu haut du ciel on fait descendre\nPour inspirer un furieux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Josué, je hais davantage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Tes sacrifices inhumains.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
