                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Donnait dans l'Italie en cendre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Des indulgences et des fers.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais de ta horde vagabonde\nDétournons mes yeux éperdus.\nO Rome ! ô maîtresse du monde !\nVerrai-je en toi quelques vertus ?\nCe n'est pas sous l'infâme Octave ;\nCe n'est pas lorsque Rome esclave\nSuccombait avec l'univers,\nOu quand le Sixième Alexandre\nDonnait dans l'Italie en cendre\nDes indulgences et des fers."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "L'innocence n'a plus d'asile :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Le sang coule à mes yeux surpris,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Depuis les vêpres de Sicile",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Jusqu'aux matines de Paris.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Est-il un peuple sur la terre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Qui dans la paix ou dans la guerre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Ait jamais vu des jours heureux ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Nous pleurons ainsi que nos pères,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Et nous transmettons nos misères",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "A nos déplorables neveux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "L'innocence n'a plus d'asile :\nLe sang coule à mes yeux surpris,\nDepuis les vêpres de Sicile\nJusqu'aux matines de Paris.\nEst-il un peuple sur la terre\nQui dans la paix ou dans la guerre\nAit jamais vu des jours heureux ?\nNous pleurons ainsi que nos pères,\nEt nous transmettons nos misères\nA nos déplorables neveux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "C'est ainsi que mon humeur sombre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Exhalait ses tristes accents ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "La nuit, me couvrant de son ombre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Avait appesanti mes sens :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Tout à coup un trait de lumière",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Ouvrit ma débile paupière,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Qui cherchait en vain le repos ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Et, des demeures éternelles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Un génie étendant ses ailes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Daigna me parler en ces mots :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est ainsi que mon humeur sombre\nExhalait ses tristes accents ;\nLa nuit, me couvrant de son ombre,\nAvait appesanti mes sens :\nTout à coup un trait de lumière\nOuvrit ma débile paupière,\nQui cherchait en vain le repos ;\nEt, des demeures éternelles,\nUn génie étendant ses ailes\nDaigna me parler en ces mots :"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "« Contemple la brillante aurore",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Qui t'annonce enfin les beaux jours :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Un nouveau monde est près d'éclore ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Até disparaît pour toujours.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Vois l'auguste Philosophie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Chez toi si longtemps poursuivie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Dicter ses triomphantes lois.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "La Vérité vient avec elle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Ouvrir la carrière immortelle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Où devaient marcher tous les rois.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Contemple la brillante aurore\nQui t'annonce enfin les beaux jours :\nUn nouveau monde est près d'éclore ;\nAté disparaît pour toujours.\nVois l'auguste Philosophie,\nChez toi si longtemps poursuivie,\nDicter ses triomphantes lois.\nLa Vérité vient avec elle\nOuvrir la carrière immortelle\nOù devaient marcher tous les rois."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Les cris affreux du fanatique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "N'épouvantent plus la raison ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "L'insidieuse Politique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "N'a plus ni masque ni poison.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "La douce, l'équitable Astrée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "S'assied, de grâces entourée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Entre le trône et les autels ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Et sa fille, la Bienfaisance,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Vient de sa corne d'abondance",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Enrichir les faibles mortels. »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les cris affreux du fanatique\nN'épouvantent plus la raison ;\nL'insidieuse Politique\nN'a plus ni masque ni poison.\nLa douce, l'équitable Astrée\nS'assied, de grâces entourée,\nEntre le trône et les autels ;\nEt sa fille, la Bienfaisance,\nVient de sa corne d'abondance\nEnrichir les faibles mortels. »"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "Je lui dis : « Ange tutélaire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
